schemas.name: description
schemas.content:
Designing a professional z-fold brochure has never been simpler! 
Just place your text and images according to the BasePDF frame, and you're ready to print. With double-sided printing, your content seamlessly flows across the panels, creating an engaging and visually appealing layout.

Automate and Customize with pdfme 
Want to generate multiple brochure variations effortlessly? 
With the pdfme library, you can dynamically replace text and images based on field names, allowing you to create countless unique brochure PDFs in no time!

Start designing today and bring your brochures to life with ease!
